parameters.content:
## SUB - Create Finish Material Sheet
Input:  { state, workspace, qb }
Output: { state, workspace, qb, fm: { sheet_id, sheet_url } }

Creates Google Sheet with header + data rows, moves to Drive subfolder.
Returns all incoming data plus fm results.

assignments.value:
={{ {
  sheet_id:  $('HTTP: Sheets - Create Spreadsheet').first().json.spreadsheetId,
  sheet_url: $('HTTP: Sheets - Create Spreadsheet').first().json.spreadsheetUrl
} }}

